wiki.content: "Kitsch" is a song recorded by South Korean girl group IVE. It was released on March 27, 2023 as the first single from their debut studio album, I've IVE. A song where you can feel the elegant beauty and unexpected charm of IVE, who is 'different because she is special'. It is a song that is fun to listen to with colorful instruments based on strong beats and bass lines, and the point is the hook that is repeated yet unexpected. It delivers a thrilling feeling by mixing various bouncy sounds, and shows the colorful charm of IVE, who is always unpredictable. The track was written by Lee Seu-ran and Hwang Hyun of MonoTree, composed by Ryan Jhun, Lise Reppe, Audun Agnar Guldbrandsen, Kyle Joseph Faulkner, Tea Carpenter, Emily Harbakk, Stally and PATEKO, and arranged by Jhun, Guldbrandsen, Stally and PATEKO.
